{
  "page": "The Winter Maid",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>\"<b>The Winter Maid</b>\" is a song sung in <a href=\"/index.php/The_North\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The North\">the North</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Winter_Maid&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Winter_Maid&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The bard <a href=\"/index.php/Abel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Abel\">Abel</a> sings \"<a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Lances\" title=\"Iron Lances\">Iron Lances</a>\" and \"The Winter Maid\" during a meal at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. When Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Barbrey_Dustin\" title=\"Barbrey Dustin\">Barbrey Dustin</a> requests something more cheerful, Abel sings \"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Queen_Took_Off_Her_Sandal,_the_King_Took_Off_His_Crown\" title=\"The Queen Took Off Her Sandal, the King Took Off His Crown\">The Queen Took Off Her Sandal, the King Took Off His Crown</a>\" and \"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Bear_and_the_Maiden_Fair\" title=\"The Bear and the Maiden Fair\">The Bear and the Maiden Fair</a>\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Winter_Maid&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, A Ghost in Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404150134\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 136/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 471/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 537/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.267      1 -total\n 77.58%    4.862      1 Template:Ref\n 55.62%    3.486      1 Template:Ref/core\n 21.21%    1.329      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:16546-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404150134 and revision id 213488\n -->\n",
